              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Kustompedia Care -->
        <div class="elementor-column elementor-col-33">
          <div class="elementor-widget-wrap">
            <div class="elementor-element elementor-widget-heading">
              <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                <h3 class="elementor-heading-title">Kustompedia Care</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="elementor-element elementor-widget-text-editor">
              <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                <p>Punya pertanyaan seputar transaksi atau bantuan lainnya?<br />Kunjungi <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?text=Saya%20dapat%20informasi%20Kustom%20Sekarang%20dari%20website%2E%20Mohon%20informasi%20lebih%20lengkap%2C%20ya%2E%20Terima%20kasih%2E" target="_blank" style="color: #FFCB01;">Kustompedia Care</a> untuk pertanyaan seputar transaksi, kelengkapan barang, repeat order, dan lain sebagainya.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Karir -->
        <div class="elementor-column elementor-col-33">
          <div class="elementor-widget-wrap">
            <div class="elementor-element elementor-widget-heading">
              <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                <h3 class="elementor-heading-title">Karir</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="elementor-element elementor-widget-text-editor">
              <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                <p>Ingin bergabung bersama tim profesional kami?<br />Kunjungi situs karir untuk menemukan pekerjaan impian dan bergabung bersama tim Kustompedia.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Row 2: Referral, FAQ, Tentang Kami -->
    <section class="elementor-section elementor-section-content-middle">
      <div class="elementor-container">
        <!-- Referral -->
        <div class="elementor-column elementor-col-33">
          <div class="elementor-widget-wrap">
            <div class="elementor-element elementor-widget-heading">
              <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                <h3 class="elementor-heading-title">Refferal</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="elementor-element elementor-widget-text-editor">
              <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                <p>Miliki penghasilan tambahan dengan bergabung bersama program affiliate Kustompedia. Tawarkan produk kami, nikmati penghasilannya!.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ -->
        <div class="elementor-column elementor-col-33">
          <div class="elementor-widget-wrap">
            <div class="elementor-element elementor-widget-heading">
              <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                <h3 class="elementor-heading-title">FAQ</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="elementor-element elementor-widget-text-editor">
              <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                <p>Ketahui informasi seputar pertanyaan yang sering diajukan secara ringkas dan praktis dalam FAQ Kustompedia ini.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tentang Kami -->
        <div class="elementor-column elementor-col-33">
          <div class="elementor-widget-wrap">
            <div class="elementor-element elementor-widget-heading">
              <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                <h3 class="elementor-heading-title">Tentang Kami</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="elementor-element elementor-widget-text-editor">
              <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                <p>Ketahui lebih banyak tentang Kustompedia. Perusahaan dan informasi terbaru mengenai kami disini.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Kantor Kami Section -->
    <div class="elementor-element elementor-container-heading">
      <div class="e-con-inner">
        <div class="elementor-element elementor-widget-heading">
          <div class="elementor-widget-container">
            <h3 class="elementor-heading-title">Kantor Kami</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="elementor-section elementor-section-content-middle">
      <div class="elementor-container">
        <div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100">
          <div class="elementor-widget-wrap">
            <!-- Google Maps -->
            <div class="elementor-element elementor-widget-google-maps">
              <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                <div class="elementor-custom-embed">
                  <iframe
                    loading="lazy"
                    src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?q=Kustompedia&amp;t=m&amp;z=16&amp;output=embed&amp;iwloc=near"
                    title="Kustompedia"
                    aria-label="Kustompedia"
                  ></iframe>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Kustom Garment -->
            <div class="elementor-element elementor-widget-heading">
              <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                <h3 class="elementor-heading-title">Kustom Garment</h3>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Address -->
            <div class="elementor-element elementor-widget-text-editor">
              <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                <p>Jl. Sidosermo IV Gg. III No. 37, Surabaya</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Elementor base styles */
  .elementor {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .elementor-element {
    position: relative;
  }

  .elementor-container-heading {
    --e-con-width: 1140px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--e-con-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .e-con-inner {
    display: block;
  }

  .elementor-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 30px 0;
  }

  .elementor-section-content-middle {
    align-items: center;
  }

  .elementor-container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1140px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .elementor-column {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .elementor-col-33 {
    width: calc(33.333% - 14px);
    min-width: 250px;
  }

  .elementor-col-100 {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .elementor-widget-wrap {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 15px;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .elementor-widget-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .elementor-heading-title {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .elementor-widget-text-editor p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .elementor-widget-text-editor a {
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .elementor-widget-text-editor a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  /* Google Maps */
  .elementor-custom-embed {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    padding-bottom: 56.25%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .elementor-custom-embed iframe {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: none;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .elementor-container-heading,
    .elementor-container {
      max-width: 100%;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .elementor-col-33 {
      width: calc(50% - 10px);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .elementor-section {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }

    .elementor-col-33 {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .elementor-heading-title {
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .elementor-widget-text-editor p {
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  }
</style>
